## How It All Connects

These concepts work together to enable effective coordination:

1. **Notes** make information visible and track who knows what
2. **Decisions** help groups converge on acceptable paths forward
3. **Commitments** coordinate action when participation depends on others

Studios and scenes provide the containers where this coordination happens, with appropriate privacy boundaries.

Subagents can participate in all of this while their parent maintains accountability for their actions.
